data.description: 3 bed 2 bath brick ranch slab home on massive corner lot in Merrymont off Columbia Rd! All kitchen appliances stay! Home boasts tons of natural light, vaulted living room ceiling, separate laundry room, and recently updated hall bath! Backyard is fully fenced in (ready for your green thumb design projects!) and includes large storage shed! Quiet neighborhood central to everything, good schools, and on the edge of a cul-de-sac! Minutes from I-20 and a straight shot to Gate 1 at Fort Eisenhauer! Minutes to Kroger, Wal-Mart, Publix, Dunkin', Starbucks, Dominos, and so much more. Come see why this should be your new home!
